inkball

Class Ball

  • java.lang.Object
    • inkball.Entity
      • inkball.Ball
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Drawable, Movable

    public class Ball
extends Entity
implements Movable, Drawable
    Represents a ball entity in the Inkball game. The ball can move, be drawn, and interact with other game entities. Each ball has a specific color, velocity, and radius.
